{"blocks":[{"key":"fieok","text":"Ordering Information","type":"header-one","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"b7lou","text":"Dicty Stock Center Distribution Policy","type":"header-three","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"egc7d","text":"The DSC fills any request from bona fide teaching or non-profit research institutions. Users from for-profit institutions need to send an email stating that the materials will be used for research only and no profit will be made from DSC materials.

We also expect the recipient to provide a FedEx, UPS, or a DHL billing number to pay for the shipping. If you create your own shipping label, please click that option. Shipping costs are third party and not related to DSC charges.

The Dicty Stock Center ships strains by default on an LPB plate with E. coli B/r as a food source.  If axenic cells in HL5 are desired, please add this information in your order.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":53,"length":10,"style":"BOLD"},{"offset":98,"length":10,"style":"BOLD"},{"offset":468,"length":11,"style":"BOLD"}],"entityRanges":[{"offset":138,"length":5,"key":0},{"offset":468,"length":11,"key":1},{"offset":536,"length":9,"key":2},{"offset":551,"length":13,"key":3},{"offset":601,"length":3,"key":4}],"data":{}},{"key":"8r9db","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"72oin","text":"Timeline","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":8,"style":"BOLD"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"anpjh","text":"Strains are plated in the order they come in as DSC orders. Depending on the order volume orders are shipped witthin a week or two, when the order is regular and small. However, if you have a small order, please remark in the comment field that you need the order as soon as possible and small orders  are preferentially plated. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"cq4ds","text":"Due to an increased order volume, we ship larger orders and GWDI orders in 2 to 4 weeks, depending on order volume. We try to bundle orders into one shipment, however, very large orders (>12) might be shipped in separate shipments. Please inquire about shipping and order returns. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"a6p6h","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"aron5","text":"Plasmids","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":8,"style":"BOLD"}],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"3j84m","text":"Plasmids will be sent as bacterial transformants on an LB (Luria Bertani) Ampicillin plate, or as DNA on a piece of filter paper by request. ","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"emt73","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"37su5","text":"Note: When you receive the strain(s) they need to be stored in the lab following one of the procedures described. New users may also consult our DSC FAQ page. Also store your plasmids following standard procedures.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[{"offset":0,"length":5,"style":"BOLD"},{"offset":145,"length":7,"style":"BOLD"}],"entityRanges":[{"offset":92,"length":10,"key":5},{"offset":145,"length":7,"key":6}],"data":{}},{"key":"7jbie","text":"Ordering Procedures for Strains or Plasmids:","type":"header-three","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"53q2a","text":"Step 1: To find the item(s) you want, search the strain or plasmid catalog.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"e7p82","text":"Step 2:  Click the green shopping cart of the available item you wish to purchase. For more details click on the strain.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"d10gj","text":"Step 3: Go to your shopping cart, inspect the items and check out.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"7m8a7","text":"Step 4: Fill out the form or login to autofill your information.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"d10i3","text":"Step 5: Complete the payment information as well and click 'Order'","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ch48d","text":"Step 6: An order confirmation will be sent by email and appears on your screen","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"4adhn","text":"","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[],"data":{}},{"key":"ag9af","text":"If you need additional assistance, please e-mail the Dicty Stock Center.","type":"unstyled","depth":0,"inlineStyleRanges":[],"entityRanges":[{"offset":53,"length":18,"key":7}],"data":{}}],"entityMap":{"0":{"type":"LINK","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"url":"mailto:dictystocks@northwestern.edu"}},"1":{"type":"LINK","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"url":"/stockcenter/information/payment"}},"2":{"type":"LINK","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"url":"/techniques/media/media.html#LPB"}},"3":{"type":"LINK","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"url":"http://dictybase.org/db/cgi-bin/dictyBase/phenotype/strain_and_phenotype_details.pl?genotype_id=6955"}},"4":{"type":"LINK","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"url":"/techniques/media/media.html#MAHL5"}},"5":{"type":"LINK","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"url":"/techniques/media/dicty_storage.html","target":"new"}},"6":{"type":"LINK","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"url":"/stockcenter/information/faq","target":"new"}},"7":{"type":"LINK","mutability":"MUTABLE","data":{"url":"mailto:dictystocks@northwestern.edu"}}}}
